
--SPA (Single Page Application)

--Router
  - listens to the events
  -DOM (Document Object Model) & HTML Rendering is done by router
  -Mapping the templates
  -HTML rendering happens at the client side
  -Dynamic Rendering
  -Not appropriate for search engines

--Typescript
  -Strongly typed language
  -Superset of javascript
  -Traspiling - .ts -> .js

--ng serve - Browser Sync (watch for the changes in your file)

--Angular Bootstraping
  -script inclusions were done as part of build process
  -main.ts -> bootstrap -> AppModule --> @NgModule (bootStrap:[AppComponent])

--Create a componnet using angular cli
  -ng generate component other
  -ng g c another --flat
  -ng g c onemore --flat --it --is (it -> inline template, is -> inline style)
